"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-surfing-wave-forecasting-paris-tahiti-b2586318.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Notifications\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"browser preferences\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 51}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in Swipe for next article French Polynesia hosts the spectacular event of surfing for the Paris 2024 Games Removed from bookmarks I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9901402175438367, \"rank\": 0.009957965824660055, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 69, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 105}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 153}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"Swipe\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 196}, {\"ngram\": \"next article\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacular event\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 258}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"bookmarks\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice The search for the perfect wave has been a part ofsurfingculture for decades, with surfers traveling from location to location in their quest for the best swells.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"The search\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect wave\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"a part ofsurfingculture\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"their quest\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the best swells\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with the development of surf forecasting- the prediction of wave swell behavior and breaking- that search has gotten much easier.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"surf\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"the prediction\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"wave swell behavior\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"that search\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, it also determines the four days that surfers competing in the ParisOlympicsinTahiti, French Polynesia, will paddle into the ocean in their pursuit for the gold medal.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9901402175438367, \"rank\": 0.009957965824660055, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polynesia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the four days\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the ParisOlympicsinTahiti\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"their pursuit\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's a look at how surf forecasting is done, how it impacts theParis 2024surfing competition and how experts expect climate change to affect future wave forecasting.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a look\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"how surf forecasting\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis 2024surfing competition\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"experts\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"future wave forecasting\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surf forecasting is often considered a branch of meteorology and oceanography as it uses the same tools and methods adopted in weather forecasting and the study of the ocean.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Surf forecasting\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"a branch\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"meteorology\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"oceanography\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"the same tools\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"methods\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"weather forecasting\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the study\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forecasters monitor wind and storms that blow over the ocean - sometimes thousands of miles out at sea - transferring their energy in the water and creating most waves.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Forecasters\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"wind\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"storms\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"miles\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"their energy\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"most waves\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They then calculate how the storms will move over the water and how long they will take to reach shores.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the storms\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"shores\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1523}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some old-school forecasters do their calculations by hand, but software has been developed to help semi-automate the data that creates forecasting models.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some old-school forecasters\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"their calculations\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"software\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"forecasting models\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forecasts can be fairly accurate up to 10 days in advance, said Nathan Cool, a wave forecaster and creator of WaveCast.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999869537534, \"rank\": 1.290371671272964e-08, \"text\": \"Nathan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nathan_Petrelli\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Forecasts\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"a wave forecaster\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"creator\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"WaveCast\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he warns that it's not an exact science.\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an exact science\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That does not stop surfers around the world from regularly checking forecasts shared on popular surfing websites to help decide if they want to surf that day.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"forecasts\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"popular surfing websites\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, but the changes are likely to be gradual rather than a shock event, said Cool.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"Cool\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's because rising seas and changes in geographic features due coastal erosion or shifting shoal shapes will change the coasts, impacting how and where waves break.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rising seas\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"changes\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"geographic features\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"shoal shapes\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"the coasts\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Features like these take long time to change, so local surfers may see less beach over time, local breaks may change, but nothing extreme in the short term,\\\" Cool said.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Features\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"long time\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"local surfers\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"less beach\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"local breaks\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"the short term\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"Cool\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But long term will see inevitable see changes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"long term\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"changes\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The surf forecast is the biggest determinant of when the Paris Olympics surfing competition will take place, predicting when swells are expected to arrive, as well as the angle and size of the waves.\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The surf forecast\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2498}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest determinant\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics surfing competition\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"swells\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only four days of a ten-day window will be allotted for the competition, so it's important to pick what forecasters think will be the best days.\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only four days\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"a ten-day window\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"forecasters\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"the best days\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The current forecast for the competition window - which spans from July 27 through August 5 - comes with good and bad news: An anticipated swell the first day in the window means the competition is anticipated to start on the first possible day.\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The current forecast\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition window\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"good and bad news\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"An anticipated swell\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"the first possible day\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the forecast also says there will be wind, negatively impacting surfing conditions and perhaps delaying competition days until later in the window.\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the forecast\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"wind\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing conditions\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"competition days\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will hope the best and plan for the worst,\\\" International Surfing Association president Fernando Aguerre told The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3275, \"end\": 3308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Surfing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Surfing_Associat